## 4. Database Schema (`olamo.db`)

**Engine:** SQLite via **`aiosqlite`** (async), **WAL mode** enabled

**4 tables** defined across 2 files:

### Table: `runs` (`/Users/anil/Source/OLamo/app/web/database.py`, lines 52-63)
| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `id` | TEXT PK | UUID |
| `description` | TEXT | Task description |
| `status` | TEXT | queued/running/interrupted/completed/failed |
| `run_id` | TEXT | Human-readable YYYYMMDD_N |
| `queued_at` | TEXT | ISO timestamp |
| `started_at` | TEXT | ISO timestamp |
| `completed_at` | TEXT | ISO timestamp |
| `error` | TEXT | Error message if failed |
| `log_dir` | TEXT | Path to log directory |
| `pr_url` | TEXT | Pull request URL |
| `settings_override` | TEXT | JSON per-run settings override |

### Table: `events` (lines 65-82)
| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `seq` | INTEGER PK AUTOINCREMENT | Monotonically increasing sequence |
| `run_id` | TEXT FK → runs(id) | |
| `ts` | TEXT | ISO timestamp |
| `data` | TEXT | Full JSON event payload |
| `type`, `stage`, `cycle`, `role`, `action` | Various | Denormalized columns for querying |
| `success`, `elapsed_ms` | INTEGER | |
| `summary`, `content_path`, `pr_url` | TEXT | |

**Index:** `idx_events_run(run_id, seq)`

### Table: `run_state` (lines 84-94)
| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `run_id` | TEXT PK | |
| `current_stage` | TEXT | Current pipeline stage |
| `current_cycle` | TEXT | Current cycle info |
| `last_agent` | TEXT | Last agent role executed |
| `last_agent_ok` | INTEGER | Whether last agent succeeded |
| `last_summary` | TEXT | Last agent result summary |
| `checkpoint_data` | TEXT | JSON checkpoint blob |
| `updated_at` | TEXT | ISO timestamp |

### Table: `agent_sessions` (`/Users/anil/Source/OLamo/app/db/sessions.py`, lines 20-31)
| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `id` | INTEGER PK AUTOINCREMENT | |
| `run_id` | TEXT | |
| `agent_name` | TEXT | |
| `role` | TEXT | |
| `session_id` | TEXT | Copilot SDK session ID |
| `settings_snapshot` | TEXT | Frozen ModelConfig JSON |
| `status` | TEXT | active/closed/expired |
| `created_at` | TEXT | |
| `closed_at` | TEXT | |

**Unique constraint:** `(run_id, role)` — one session per agent per run.

