## 6. Agent Types in `agents/` Directory

**Path:** `/Users/anil/Source/OLamo/agents/`

### Character Files (system prompts):
| File | Role | Purpose |
|------|------|---------|
| `lead-developer.md` | **Lead Developer** | Planning (3 modes: Plan, Refine, Review Implementation). Does NOT write code. |
| `developer.md` | **Developer** | Code implementation exactly per spec. Fixes issues/build failures only. |
| `code-reviewer.md` | **Code Reviewer** | Bug/security/performance/quality review after implementation. |
| `qa-engineer.md` | **QA Engineer** | Design review (testability) + Code review (PASS/FAIL per scenario). |
| `build-agent.md` | **Build Agent** | Deploys, builds, compiles, smoke tests. Reports SUCCESS/FAILURE. |
| `repo-manager.md` | **Repo Manager** | 5 modes: commit+PR, poll PR comments, push changes, mark comments addressed, poll CI checks. |

### Prompt Templates: `/Users/anil/Source/OLamo/agents/prompts/`
Contains per-role task templates (e.g., `prompts/pm/pipeline.md` for the PM system prompt) with `{{token}}` placeholder substitution.

